body:
@onizmx Correct, I am just looking at the diff at the moment and trying to find the reason. One thing that looks promising is the new buffer size configurations: https://github.com/redis/go-redis?tab=readme-ov-file#buffer-size-configuration
Can you pleaase try by setting the buffer to a smaller size, previously the default as the default of go - 4096 https://github.com/golang/go/blob/master/src/bufio/bufio.go#L19 and now is 524288, which will make sense why you see the initial increase.

Feel free to drop it back to `4096` with the configuration and check if you observe any increase in the usage that look like potential memory leak.
